snippet.title: Projected Dreams - Official Release Window Trailer | WLG Showcase 2025
snippet.description: Drag toys from the shelves and drop them on the table to create a shadow play in this cozy puzzle game. As the shadows unfold, immerse yourself in a heartwarming story full of nostalgia from the 90s and blur the lines between fantasy and reality. Projected Dreams will be available on PC in spring 2025.
